{"tid":951612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"酒池肉林21世紀版　杭州酒店推巨型鴛鴦火鍋溫泉　網民：辣腫下體","createTime":"2018-12-22T13:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T06:46:07.000Z","uid":66271,"like":355,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"d82d85ebc35a48cb4238155337c3b096edd99b85","tid":951612,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:06:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/273392/%E9%85%92%E6%B1%A0%E8%82%89%E6%9E%9721%E4%B8%96%E7%B4%80%E7%89%88-%E6%9D%AD%E5%B7%9E%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E6%8E%A8%E5%B7%A8%E5%9E%8B%E9%B4%9B%E9%B4%A6%E7%81%AB%E9%8D%8B%E6%BA%AB%E6%B3%89-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E8%BE%A3%E8%85%AB%E4%B8%8B%E9%AB%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F273392%2F%25E9%2585%2592%25E6%25B1%25A0%25E8%2582%2589%25E6%259E%259721%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%25B4%2580%25E7%2589%2588-%25E6%259D%25AD%25E5%25B7%259E%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%25B7%25A8%25E5%259E%258B%25E9%25B4%259B%25E9%25B4%25A6%25E7%2581%25AB%25E9%258D%258B%25E6%25BA%25AB%25E6%25B3%2589-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E8%25BE%25A3%25E8%2585%25AB%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%25AB%2594&d=Hrp0fs57trArtuevVMsA6viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a8b2d87b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/273392/%E9%85%92%E6%B1%A0%E8%82%89%E6%9E%9721%E4%B8%96%E7%B4%80%E7%89%88-%E6%9D%AD%E5%B7%9E%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E6%8E%A8%E5%B7%A8%E5%9E%8B%E9%B4%9B%E9%B4%A6%E7%81%AB%E9%8D%8B%E6%BA%AB%E6%B3%89-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E8%BE%A3%E8%85%AB%E4%B8%8B%E9%AB%94</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2231230/org/161e2a8f4092ca4196d7b379b00d6789.jpg/lkh1hktj7wyd75fpiIdPWR2b_pRw9hEywU-jIsFPoyI?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2231230%2Forg%2F161e2a8f4092ca4196d7b379b00d6789.jpg%2Flkh1hktj7wyd75fpiIdPWR2b_pRw9hEywU-jIsFPoyI%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=ff3a8f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n火鍋配料多不勝數，原來除了豬牛羊雞還有「人」？杭州天氣漸冷，一間酒店有新噱頭，推出直徑5米的「鴛鴦火鍋溫泉」，一半放辣椒，一半放生菜、菇菌等養生佐料，讓市民在冬天浸在火鍋中，一邊泡溫泉，同時在池邊享受火鍋美食。不過許多網民對這樣子吃火鍋不太受落，不但追問泉中食物能不能吃，更擔心問道：「下體會不會辣腫？」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2230788/org/66434f64b0acc13c196697595043cada.jpg/d7y_bTt-ghQ7g5EIbRiDa8YOwZ1pbQiyNVTLKDVUyyg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2230788%2Forg%2F66434f64b0acc13c196697595043cada.jpg%2Fd7y_bTt-ghQ7g5EIbRiDa8YOwZ1pbQiyNVTLKDVUyyg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6cc6ca8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n杭州第一世界大酒店雲曼溫泉在周日（16日）推出一個直徑5米的巨型「鴛鴦火鍋溫泉」，讓遊客可以穿泳裝浸泡，這個火鍋一半放滿辣椒，另一邊放滿生菜、菌菇、枸杞等養生佐料。池中就放滿一個個火鍋，讓遊客一邊泡溫泉一邊開餐。<br />\n<br />\n酒店表示，這個火鍋是暖冬節推出的系列活動之一，稱「季進補，來年打虎，適度泡溫泉可以使肌肉、關節鬆弛，消除疲勞，還可以擴張血管，促進血液迴圈，加速人體新陳代謝」，而一邊泡溫泉一邊吃養生火鍋是「從未感受過的新奇火鍋體驗」。酒店員工更會扮成嫦娥等角色為客人傳菜，場面十分搞笑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2230802/org/c7fa9aaeb16022670328ecb077336a3d.jpg/kPCcM-P3QdniaPq5zLFliG_bNalnuuEY7pLure6S7q0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2230802%2Forg%2Fc7fa9aaeb16022670328ecb077336a3d.jpg%2FkPCcM-P3QdniaPq5zLFliG_bNalnuuEY7pLure6S7q0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=863f9a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2230821/org/eb727c92be09aed6bace0bab5c3181fa.jpg/nfcBlh_J7i1SjHg_JQ34ZIYYfl-dKrrWAoqGewKKhns\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2230821%2Forg%2Feb727c92be09aed6bace0bab5c3181fa.jpg%2FnfcBlh_J7i1SjHg_JQ34ZIYYfl-dKrrWAoqGewKKhns&h=cb680024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2230820/org/68526f1f61dcbf71c330e9aa8dbdc80f.jpg/l19XXHMiVo-o2NzYOoYaPbEOBDb6uyuC1lxgJtZcYCY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2230820%2Forg%2F68526f1f61dcbf71c330e9aa8dbdc80f.jpg%2Fl19XXHMiVo-o2NzYOoYaPbEOBDb6uyuC1lxgJtZcYCY&h=3e7ff961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJM9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98dbf4a2b7774983b379a5f9bee8984c8e63dfcc","tid":951612,"uid":13008,"like":0,"dislike":58,"score":-58,"quote":{"pid":"d82d85ebc35a48cb4238155337c3b096edd99b85","tid":951612,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:06:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/273392/%E9%85%92%E6%B1%A0%E8%82%89%E6%9E%9721%E4%B8%96%E7%B4%80%E7%89%88-%E6%9D%AD%E5%B7%9E%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E6%8E%A8%E5%B7%A8%E5%9E%8B%E9%B4%9B%E9%B4%A6%E7%81%AB%E9%8D%8B%E6%BA%AB%E6%B3%89-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E8%BE%A3%E8%85%AB%E4%B8%8B%E9%AB%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F273392%2F%25E9%2585%2592%25E6%25B1%25A0%25E8%2582%2589%25E6%259E%259721%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%25B4%2580%25E7%2589%2588-%25E6%259D%25AD%25E5%25B7%259E%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%25B7%25A8%25E5%259E%258B%25E9%25B4%259B%25E9%25B4%25A6%25E7%2581%25AB%25E9%258D%258B%25E6%25BA%25AB%25E6%25B3%2589-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E8%25BE%25A3%25E8%2585%25AB%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%25AB%2594&d=Hrp0fs57trArtuevVMsA6viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a8b2d87b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/273392/%E9%85%92%E6%B1%A0%E8%82%89%E6%9E%9721%E4%B8%96%E7%B4%80%E7%89%88-%E6%9D%AD%E5%B7%9E%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E6%8E%A8%E5%B7%A8%E5%9E%8B%E9%B4%9B%E9%B4%A6%E7%81%AB%E9%8D%8B%E6%BA%AB%E6%B3%89-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E8%BE%A3%E8%85%AB%E4%B8%8B%E9%AB%94</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2231230/org/161e2a8f4092ca4196d7b379b00d6789.jpg/lkh1hktj7wyd75fpiIdPWR2b_pRw9hEywU-jIsFPoyI?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2231230%2Forg%2F161e2a8f4092ca4196d7b379b00d6789.jpg%2Flkh1hktj7wyd75fpiIdPWR2b_pRw9hEywU-jIsFPoyI%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=ff3a8f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n火鍋配料多不勝數，原來除了豬牛羊雞還有「人」？杭州天氣漸冷，一間酒店有新噱頭，推出直徑5米的「鴛鴦火鍋溫泉」，一半放辣椒，一半放生菜、菇菌等養生佐料，讓市民在冬天浸在火鍋中，一邊泡溫泉，同時在池邊享受火鍋美食。不過許多網民對這樣子吃火鍋不太受落，不但追問泉中食物能不能吃，更擔心問道：「下體會不會辣腫？」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2230788/org/66434f64b0acc13c196697595043cada.jpg/d7y_bTt-ghQ7g5EIbRiDa8YOwZ1pbQiyNVTLKDVUyyg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2230788%2Forg%2F66434f64b0acc13c196697595043cada.jpg%2Fd7y_bTt-ghQ7g5EIbRiDa8YOwZ1pbQiyNVTLKDVUyyg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6cc6ca8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n杭州第一世界大酒店雲曼溫泉在周日（16日）推出一個直徑5米的巨型「鴛鴦火鍋溫泉」，讓遊客可以穿泳裝浸泡，這個火鍋一半放滿辣椒，另一邊放滿生菜、菌菇、枸杞等養生佐料。池中就放滿一個個火鍋，讓遊客一邊泡溫泉一邊開餐。<br />\n<br />\n酒店表示，這個火鍋是暖冬節推出的系列活動之一，稱「季進補，來年打虎，適度泡溫泉可以使肌肉、關節鬆弛，消除疲勞，還可以擴張血管，促進血液迴圈，加速人體新陳代謝」，而一邊泡溫泉一邊吃養生火鍋是「從未感受過的新奇火鍋體驗」。酒店員工更會扮成嫦娥等角色為客人傳菜，場面十分搞笑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2230802/org/c7fa9aaeb16022670328ecb077336a3d.jpg/kPCcM-P3QdniaPq5zLFliG_bNalnuuEY7pLure6S7q0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2230802%2Forg%2Fc7fa9aaeb16022670328ecb077336a3d.jpg%2FkPCcM-P3QdniaPq5zLFliG_bNalnuuEY7pLure6S7q0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=863f9a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2230821/org/eb727c92be09aed6bace0bab5c3181fa.jpg/nfcBlh_J7i1SjHg_JQ34ZIYYfl-dKrrWAoqGewKKhns\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2230821%2Forg%2Feb727c92be09aed6bace0bab5c3181fa.jpg%2FnfcBlh_J7i1SjHg_JQ34ZIYYfl-dKrrWAoqGewKKhns&h=cb680024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2230820/org/68526f1f61dcbf71c330e9aa8dbdc80f.jpg/l19XXHMiVo-o2NzYOoYaPbEOBDb6uyuC1lxgJtZcYCY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A